verses.verse: A Psalm of David. <S%H3051>Ascribe<s%> unto <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>, O ye sons of the <S%H1121>mighty<s%>, <S%H3051>Ascribe<s%> unto <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> <S%H3519>glory<s%> and <S%H5797>strength<s%>.
Ascribe <S%H3051><s%> unto <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> the <S%H3519>glory<s%> due unto his <S%H8034>name<s%>; <S%H7812>Worship<s%> <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> in <S%H6944>holy<s%> <S%H1927>array<s%>.

The <S%H6963>voice<s%> of <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> is upon the <S%H4325>waters<s%>: The <S%H410>God<s%> of <S%H3519>glory<s%> <S%H7481>thundereth<s%>, Even <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> upon <S%H7227>many<s%> <S%H4325>waters<s%>.
The <S%H6963>voice<s%> of <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> is <S%H3581>powerful<s%>; The <S%H6963>voice<s%> of <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> is full of <S%H1926>majesty<s%>.
The <S%H6963>voice<s%> of <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> <S%H7665>breaketh<s%> the <S%H730>cedars<s%>; <S%H3068>Yea<s%>, Jehovah <S%H7665>breaketh<s%> in pieces the <S%H730>cedars<s%> of <S%H3844>Lebanon<s%>.
He maketh them also to <S%H7540>skip<s%> like a <S%H5695>calf<s%>; <S%H3844>Lebanon<s%> and <S%H8303>Sirion<s%> like a <S%H1121>young<s%> <S%H7214>wild-ox<s%>.

The <S%H6963>voice<s%> of <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> maketh the <S%H355>hinds<s%> to <S%H2342>calve<s%>, And <S%H2834>strippeth<s%> the <S%H3295>forests<s%> <S%H1964>bare<s%>: And in his temple everything <S%H559>saith<s%>, <S%H3519>Glory<s%>.
Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> <S%H3427>sat<s%> as King at the <S%H3999>Flood<s%>; <S%H3068>Yea<s%>, Jehovah <S%H3427>sitteth<s%> as <S%H4428>King<s%> for <S%H5769>ever<s%>.
Jehovah <S%H3068><s%> will <S%H5414>give<s%> <S%H5797>strength<s%> unto his <S%H5971>people<s%>; <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> will <S%H1288>bless<s%> his <S%H5971>people<s%> with <S%H7965>peace<s%>.
